TY  - JOUR
T1  - On the Limits of Communication in Multidimensional Cheap Talk: A Comment
AU  - Levy, Gilat
AU  - Razin, Ronny
Y1  - 2007/05/01
PY  - 2007
DA  - 2007/05/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1468-0262.2007.00771.x
