JF  - Econometrica
JO  - Econometrica
SP  - 885
EP  - 893
VL  - 75
IS  - 3
KW  - Cheap talk
KW  - multidimensional policy space
KW  - large conflicts
PB  - John Wiley & Sons, Ltd
SN  - 0012-9682
UR  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1468-0262.2007.00771.x
Y2  - 2024/03/26
N2  - We analyze a cheap talk game, à la Crawford and Sobel, in a multidimensional state and policy space. A feature of the multidimensional state space is that communication on one dimension often reveals information on others. We show how this feature imposes bounds on communication.
ER  - 

